
---

### .gitignore

Here's a basic `.gitignore` file to ignore unnecessary files and folders:

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Logs
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Environment variables
.env

# Build files
build/

# OS-specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE-specific files
.vscode/
.idea/

# Frontend files
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/build/
frontend/.env.local
frontend/.env.development.local
frontend/.env.test.local
frontend/.env.production.local

# Backend files
backend/node_modules/
backend/.env
backend/.env.local
backend/.env.development.local
backend/.env.test.local
backend/.env.production.local
